The paper deals with a new cryptographic primitive, which is likely to fall under the category of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the potential application of the primitive in Anonymous Credentials and the Database Aggregation Problem, which suggests that it could also belong to the sub-categories of Computational Complexity (cs.CC), Information Theory (cs.IT), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Databases (cs.DB).
